data.description: Welcome Home! This 2018 build with charming rocking chair front porch can be found in sought after Great Sky! Office/flex space through foyer to your left upon entry with dining room to your right! Open concept from living room into eat-in kitchen boasting of granite countertops and SS appliances. Pergola under oversized slab welcomes you into the fenced-in back yard with cozy fie pit + plenty of room for outdoor entertaining. Upstairs leads to all bedrooms + bonus loft space! Primary bedroom boasts of huge bathroom w/ separate soaking tub + shower; walk-in closet and double vanity. Secondary bedroom sizes will not disappoint + plenty of closet and storage space throughout! Prime location with all the amenities you've been looking for!
